## Package-Specific Guidelines

### Core Package (`packages/core/`)
- Use `testTheme` for theme-related tests
- Use `customTheme` for custom theme tests
- Use `WORKSPACE_FIXTURE` for complex workspace scenarios
- Test property processing, compute functions, and theme integration

### Factory Package (`packages/factory/`)
- Use real workspace data for export tests
- Test code generation with actual component structures
- Verify asset processing with real file paths and data
- Test validation with realistic component schemas

### Components Package (`packages/components/`)
- Test component schemas with real property structures
- Use actual component IDs and levels
- Test component hierarchy and relationships
- Verify component instantiation with real data
